{"text_id":3085,"tokens":["We"," investigate"," the"," phenomenon"," of"," vortex"," trapping"," in"," suddenly"," connected"," Bose","-","Joseph","son"," junctions",","," a"," long","-","standing"," problem"," in"," condensed"," matter"," physics","."," The"," rapid"," switching"," of"," a"," Joseph","son"," junction"," between"," its"," superconducting"," and"," normal"," states"," can"," lead"," to"," the"," formation"," of"," a"," vortex"," lattice",","," which"," significantly"," affects"," the"," device","'","s"," behavior","."," However",","," the"," dynamics"," of"," vortex"," trapping"," in"," such"," junctions"," remain"," poorly"," understood",","," hindering"," the"," design"," and"," optimization"," of"," vortex","-","based"," quantum"," devices","."," We"," address"," this"," challenge"," by"," developing"," a"," theoretical"," framework"," that"," combines"," the"," Gin","zburg","-","Land","au"," theory"," with"," a"," dynamic"," variational"," approach","."," Our"," methodology"," allows"," us"," to"," accurately"," capture"," the"," complex"," interplay"," between"," the"," electromagnetic"," fields",","," the"," superconducting"," condensate",","," and"," the"," vortex"," dynamics","."," We"," find"," that"," the"," vortex"," trapping"," is"," characterized"," by"," a"," distinct"," crossover"," from"," a"," diff","usive"," to"," a"," localized"," regime",","," which"," is"," governed"," by"," the"," ratio"," of"," the"," junction","'","s"," parameters"," and"," the"," strength"," of"," the"," applied"," magnetic"," field","."," Our"," results"," provide"," a"," detailed"," understanding"," of"," the"," vortex"," trapping"," mechanism",","," which"," can"," be"," exploited"," to"," enhance"," the"," performance"," of"," vortex","-","based"," quantum"," devices"," and"," facilitate"," their"," integration"," into"," future"," quantum"," computing"," architectures","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"llama3-8b","label":1}